16:59.200 --> 17:03.640
The simple message would be,
let's get back to wood.

17:03.640 --> 17:06.400
Simple wooden toys.

17:06.400 --> 17:12.400
For simple...people, children.
It's very early days.

17:15.599 --> 17:18.800
