will tighten that up a bit.

17:18.800 --> 17:25.680
So? Good? Good. Good.

17:25.680 --> 17:28.079
Good. Fine.

17:28.079 --> 17:29.960
Good.

17:29.960 --> 17:32.440
Funny old department
to come into, isn't it?

17:32.440 --> 17:39.800
Obviously you shied away from
